Program: Outlook
Title: Aborting Female Babies in India
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03kbrxh
Last Broadcast Date: Not available
A campaign in India to stop babies being aborted because they are girls. Family secrets including a listener who was adopted finding his biological family and a woman whose great-grandfather was in the Ku Klux Klan. An interracial Zimbabwean couple on writing a biography of Seretse Khama and his white wife Ruth Presenter: Heather Payton. Show less